{"data":{"page":{"id":"abd9f074-2ce6-57b4-a854-80d1227adc43","html":"<p class=\"work-links\">\n<a class=\"btn icon icon-external\" href=\"http://work.joanmira.com/webs/ivantorres\" target=\"_blank\">Launch archived website</a>\n</p>\n<p>A friend of mine, Iván Torres, asked me to build a website to showcase his portfolio of drawings, illustrations and other graphic design projects. He required a custom Flash design with a CMS feature to upload new images.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.3%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/08820bad030588e05ddcc772a0767e36/6b333/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/08820bad030588e05ddcc772a0767e36/f3ce7/1.jpg 200w,\n/static/08820bad030588e05ddcc772a0767e36/72342/1.jpg 400w,\n/static/08820bad030588e05ddcc772a0767e36/6b333/1.jpg 800w,\n/static/08820bad030588e05ddcc772a0767e36/40247/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 52.900000000000006%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/e5760c7ad8c9a828c2c05c5f6ae4ebad/6b333/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e5760c7ad8c9a828c2c05c5f6ae4ebad/f3ce7/2.jpg 200w,\n/static/e5760c7ad8c9a828c2c05c5f6ae4ebad/72342/2.jpg 400w,\n/static/e5760c7ad8c9a828c2c05c5f6ae4ebad/6b333/2.jpg 800w,\n/static/e5760c7ad8c9a828c2c05c5f6ae4ebad/40247/2.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>The admin panel password is ‘arturo’. All controls are disabled.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 59.3%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/ad95a9e9066a7a94da3ea457ab731295/6b333/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ad95a9e9066a7a94da3ea457ab731295/f3ce7/3.jpg 200w,\n/static/ad95a9e9066a7a94da3ea457ab731295/72342/3.jpg 400w,\n/static/ad95a9e9066a7a94da3ea457ab731295/6b333/3.jpg 800w,\n/static/ad95a9e9066a7a94da3ea457ab731295/40247/3.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    